  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Kitchen helper",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support chefs by preparing ingredients, maintaining kitchen cleanliness, and assisting with basic cooking tasks to ensure smooth kitchen operations and compliance with food safety standards.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare ingredients by washing, cutting, marinating, and processing them to meet recipe requirements for hot dishes, cold dishes, and soups</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of kitchen workstations, equipment, and utensils following SFA food safety standards</li><li>Assist chefs with plating and simple cooking tasks under supervision to ensure timely food preparation</li><li>Manage stock rotation, ingredient storage, and labeling to maintain kitchen inventory accuracy and freshness</li><li>Wash dishes and kitchen tools and keep the kitchen area clean to support overall kitchen hygiene</li><li>Follow kitchen standard operating procedures (SOPs), food safety, and workplace safety regulations to maintain a safe working environment</li><li>Collaborate with the kitchen team to complete other assigned duties efficiently and effectively</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience working in a Chinese kitchen environment</li><li>Ability to work efficiently in a fast-paced kitchen setting</li><li>Basic knowledge of kitchen hygiene and food safety practices</li><li>Willingness to learn new skills and follow instructions</li><li>Physical fitness to stand for extended periods during shifts</li><li>Positive attitude and ability to work well within a team</li></ul>",
